msgstr "ວະລີຜ່ານການເຂົ້າລະຫັດສຳລັບ %s"

#: monitor/udisks2/gvfsudisks2volume.c:1492
msgid "A passphrase is required to access the volume"
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການວະລີຜ່ານເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງໂວລຸມ"

#. Translators: %s is the description of the volume that is being unlocked
#: monitor/udisks2/gvfsudisks2volume.c:1507
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Authentication Required\n"
"A passphrase is needed to access encrypted data on “%s”.\n"
"The volume might be a VeraCrypt volume as it contains random data."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ\nຕ້ອງການວະລີຜ່ານເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດໃນ “%s”.\nໂວລຸມນີ້ອາດເປັນໂວລຸມ VeraCrypt ເນື່ອງຈາກມັນມີຂໍ້ມູນແບບສຸ່ມ."

#. Translators: %s is the description of the volume that is being unlocked
#: monitor/udisks2/gvfsudisks2volume.c:1513
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Authentication Required\n"
"A passphrase is needed to access encrypted data on “%s”."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ\nຕ້ອງການວະລີຜ່ານເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດໃນ “%s”."

#. Translators: this is used to describe the drive the encrypted media
#. * is on - the first %s is the name (such as 'WD 2500JB External'), the
#. * second %s is the description ('250 GB Hard Disk').
#.
#: monitor/udisks2/gvfsudisks2volume.c:1693
#, c-format
msgid "%s (%s)"
msgstr "%s (%s)"

